    "description": "<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">This </span><span class=\"s2\">School of</span><span class=\"s1\"> magic is concerned with mastery of fire, including heat and its absence. Wizards adept in this </span><span class=\"s2\">School of</span><span class=\"s1\"> magic often gain a rather unfair reputation for a lack of subtlety. Spells from this School require strong, clear gestures to be cast, as well as words of power.</span></p>\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Spontaneous Casting Complexities</span></h2>\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 85px;\" border=\"1\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 12.6633%;\"><col style=\"width: 87.3367%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px;\"><strong>Complexity</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px;\"><strong>Effect</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px;\">0</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Ignite flammable objects; inflict Health damage with fire</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px;\">1</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Extinguish a small fire</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 17px;\">2</td>\n<td style=\"height: 17px;\">\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Heat or chill an object; create closely-controlled fire</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>",
